{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1166,"text":"So, Ma was trying to explain\nsomething to me"},{"time":3463,"text":"about Grandma and when they grew up,"},{"time":5278,"text":"but I couldn't pay attention to her"},{"time":7009,"text":"because I was five years old,\nand I was petrified."},{"time":9965,"text":"I had just seen The Green Lady."},{"time":12974,"text":"Now, about a week earlier,\nI'd watched that movie \"Godzilla,\""},{"time":15997,"text":"the one about that huge lizard-like beast\nstorming a major city,"},{"time":19168,"text":"and the thought of a green monster\ncoming for me was stuck in my mind."},{"time":23850,"text":"And yet there I was,\nat the tip of Lower Manhattan with my mom,"},{"time":27163,"text":"just staring at her:"},{"time":28968,"text":"her horns,"},{"time":30151,"text":"her muscles --"},{"time":31336,"text":"all of it just frightened me."},{"time":32741,"text":"And I didn't know\nwhether she was a monster or a hero."},{"time":37138,"text":"So I decided to consult\nthe Google of the day --"},{"time":40384,"text":"\"Ma! Ma!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":41688,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":43608,"text":"My mother explained that The Green Lady\nis actually the Statue of Liberty"},{"time":48073,"text":"and that she was waving immigrants in."},{"time":50368,"text":"Now, the part of her explanation\nthat really messed with my young head"},{"time":54687,"text":"was the fact that, according to Ma,"},{"time":57346,"text":"long before us,"},{"time":59403,"text":"The Green Lady was actually brown,"},{"time":63202,"text":"brown like me,"},{"time":64579,"text":"and that she changed\ncolors over the years,"},{"time":67904,"text":"much like America."},{"time":69262,"text":"Now, the part that really\nis intriguing about this"},{"time":74580,"text":"is that when she changed colors,"},{"time":76235,"text":"she made me think about myself."},{"time":78481,"text":"It all made sense to me,"},{"time":79900,"text":"because as a first-generation American,"},{"time":81921,"text":"I was surrounded by immigrants."},{"time":83422,"text":"In fact, within my immediate social circle\nof the people who support me,"},{"time":87256,"text":"who enrich my life,"},{"time":88568,"text":"at least two are foreign-born."},{"time":91199,"text":"My life as a US citizen is in many ways\nshaped by newcomers,"},{"time":94875,"text":"and chances are,"},{"time":96058,"text":"so is yours."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97534,"text":"There are more than 40 million\nimmigrants in the USA."},{"time":101211,"text":"According to census data,"},{"time":102745,"text":"a quarter of the nation's children\nhave at least one foreign-born parent."},{"time":107431,"text":"I know all these statistics\nbecause I study global migration patterns."},{"time":112566,"text":"I'm a journalist,\nand for the last few years,"},{"time":114752,"text":"I've been documenting\nthe lives of US citizens"},{"time":117183,"text":"who've lost people to deportation."},{"time":119135,"text":"And the numbers are enormous."},{"time":122036,"text":"From 2008 to 2016,"},{"time":124608,"text":"more than three million people\nwere \"ordered removed\" --"},{"time":127926,"text":"that's the technical term\nfor being deported."},{"time":131415,"text":"There is an economic, a political,\na psychological and an emotional cost"},{"time":136956,"text":"to those deportations --"},{"time":138876,"text":"the moments when these circles are broken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141702,"text":"I once asked a US soldier,"},{"time":143472,"text":"\"Why did you volunteer to fight this war?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":145831,"text":"And she told me,"},{"time":147034,"text":"\"Because I'm proud to defend my country.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":149044,"text":"But I pressed to know --"},{"time":150234,"text":"\"Really, when you're on base,"},{"time":152115,"text":"and you hear bombs\nexploding in the distance,"},{"time":154378,"text":"and you see soldiers coming back\nwho are gravely injured,"},{"time":158179,"text":"in that moment,\nwhen you know you could be next,"},{"time":162362,"text":"what does 'my country' mean?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":164806,"text":"She looked at me."},{"time":166568,"text":"\"My country is my wife,"},{"time":168459,"text":"my family,"},{"time":169797,"text":"my friends, my soldiers.\""},{"time":171381,"text":"What she was telling me"},{"time":172722,"text":"is that \"my country\" is a collection\nof these strong relationships;"},{"time":176114,"text":"these social circles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178406,"text":"When the social circles are weakened,"},{"time":180650,"text":"a country itself is weaker."},{"time":183255,"text":"We're missing a crucial aspect\nin the debate about immigration policy."},{"time":186869,"text":"Rather than focusing on individuals,"},{"time":188916,"text":"we should focus\non the circles around them,"},{"time":191967,"text":"because these are the people\nwho are left behind:"},{"time":194980,"text":"the voters, the taxpayers,"},{"time":196884,"text":"the ones who are suffering that loss."},{"time":199186,"text":"And it's not just the children\nof the deported"},{"time":201492,"text":"who are impacted."},{"time":202857,"text":"You have brothers and sisters\nwho are separated by borders."},{"time":205758,"text":"You have classmates, teachers,\nlaw enforcement officers,"},{"time":208589,"text":"technologists, scientists, doctors,"},{"time":210845,"text":"who are all scrambling\nto make sense of new realities"},{"time":214587,"text":"when their social circles are broken."},{"time":217885,"text":"These are the real lives\nbehind all these statistics"},{"time":221564,"text":"that dominate discussions\nabout immigration policy."},{"time":224036,"text":"But we don't often think about them."},{"time":226021,"text":"And I'm trying to change that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227917,"text":"Here's just one of the real-life stories\nthat I've collected."},{"time":232550,"text":"And it still haunts me."},{"time":234482,"text":"I met Ramon and his son in 2016,"},{"time":238251,"text":"the same year both of them\nwere being ordered out of the country."},{"time":242459,"text":"Ramon was being deported to Latin America,"},{"time":246373,"text":"while his son, who was a sergeant\nin the US military,"},{"time":249722,"text":"was being deployed."},{"time":252596,"text":"Deported ..."},{"time":254479,"text":"deployed."},{"time":256308,"text":"If you just look at Ramon's case,"},{"time":259318,"text":"it wouldn't be clear how deeply\nconnected to the country he is."},{"time":263307,"text":"But consider his son:"},{"time":265159,"text":"a US citizen defending a country\nthat's banished his father."},{"time":269499,"text":"The social circle is what's key here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271955,"text":"Here's another example\nthat illustrates those critical bonds."},{"time":275408,"text":"A group of citizens in Philadelphia\nwere concerned about their jobs,"},{"time":278770,"text":"because the legal owner\nof the restaurant where they worked"},{"time":281785,"text":"was an undocumented immigrant,"},{"time":283549,"text":"and immigration officials\nhad picked him up."},{"time":286218,"text":"They rallied behind him."},{"time":287585,"text":"An immigration lawyer argued"},{"time":289032,"text":"he was too important\nto the local community"},{"time":291230,"text":"to be deported."},{"time":292702,"text":"At the hearing, they even submitted\nrestaurant reviews --"},{"time":296784,"text":"restaurant reviews!"},{"time":298645,"text":"In the end, a judge exercised\nwhat's called \"judicial discretion\""},{"time":303337,"text":"and allowed him to stay in the country,"},{"time":305297,"text":"but only because they considered\nthe social circle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309647,"text":"There are 23 million\nnoncitizens in the USA,"},{"time":314434,"text":"according to verifiable federal data."},{"time":316526,"text":"And that doesn't include the undocumented,"},{"time":318712,"text":"because numbers for that population\nare at best complex estimates."},{"time":322090,"text":"Let's just work with what we have."},{"time":324372,"text":"That's 23 million social circles --"},{"time":327438,"text":"about 100 million individuals"},{"time":330367,"text":"whose lives could be impacted\nby deportation."},{"time":333490,"text":"And the stress of it all is trickling down\nthrough the population."},{"time":337341,"text":"A 2017 poll by UCLA of LA County residents"},{"time":340986,"text":"found that 30 percent\nof citizens in LA County"},{"time":344783,"text":"are stressed about deportation,"},{"time":347128,"text":"not because they themselves\ncould be removed,"},{"time":350128,"text":"but rather, because members\nof their social circle were at risk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355823,"text":"I am not suggesting that no one\nshould ever be deported;"},{"time":358542,"text":"don't confuse me with that."},{"time":360417,"text":"But what I am saying is that we need\nto look at the bigger picture."},{"time":365692,"text":"If you are within the sound of my voice,"},{"time":368069,"text":"I want you to close your eyes for a moment"},{"time":370543,"text":"and examine your own social circle."},{"time":373923,"text":"Who are your foreign-born?"},{"time":376120,"text":"What would it feel like\nif the circle were broken?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":380488,"text":"Share your story."},{"time":382550,"text":"I'm building a global archive\nof first-person accounts"},{"time":385198,"text":"and linking them with mapping technology,"},{"time":387483,"text":"so that we can see exactly\nwhere these circles break,"},{"time":391411,"text":"because this is not\njust an American issue."},{"time":394816,"text":"There are a quarter-billion migrants\naround the world;"},{"time":398061,"text":"people living, loving and learning\nin countries where they were not born."},{"time":402160,"text":"And in my career, in my life,\nI've been one of them:"},{"time":404816,"text":"in China, in Africa, in Europe."},{"time":407822,"text":"And each time I become\none of these foreigners --"},{"time":410996,"text":"one of these strange-looking\nguys in a new land --"},{"time":414173,"text":"I can't help but think back to that day"},{"time":416166,"text":"when I was in Lower Manhattan with my mom"},{"time":418546,"text":"all those decades ago,"},{"time":420474,"text":"when I was scared,"},{"time":422096,"text":"and I had just spotted that green lady."},{"time":425624,"text":"And I guess the question\nthat I keep on thinking about"},{"time":429754,"text":"when I see her"},{"time":431030,"text":"and all the younger replicas of her\nthat are so obviously brown,"},{"time":435314,"text":"and even the paintings\nthat showcase her in the beginning"},{"time":438151,"text":"as not quite green --"},{"time":441532,"text":"when I look at all of that,"},{"time":444038,"text":"the question that my research\nseeks to answer"},{"time":447410,"text":"becomes, to me, the same one\nthat confounded me all those years ago:"},{"time":452652,"text":"Is she a monster"},{"time":455011,"text":"or a hero?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":457271,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":458445,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}